421
00:25:39,559 --> 00:25:41,160
Tandaan na pakainin si Fa Cai.

422
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,400
Huwag mong patuloy na pakainin si Yao Ji.

423
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:44,200
